    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a requirement to activate this jutsu, you must currently be in the Great Weapon Stance. Your eyes glaze over with a blood fueled fury,  for but a moment.</p><p>Make one melee taijutsu attack using your weapon, dealing your weapons damage + 4d8, rerolling all 1's and 2's, taking the second result even if it is a 1 or 2.</p><p>Additionally, if you score a critical hit with this attack you add your level to the damage dealt.  </p>",
